import React from "react"
import './App.css'
import {NavLink} from "react-router-dom"

const Navbar = () =>{
  
  return(
    <>
    <NavLink className="nav" exact activeClassName="ac" to="/">Home</NavLink>
    <NavLink  className="nav" exact activeClassName="ac" to="/about">About</NavLink>
    <NavLink className="nav" exact activeClassName="ac" to="/stock">Stock</NavLink>
    <NavLink  className="nav" exact activeClassName="ac" to="/contact">Contact</NavLink>
    </>
  )
}

export default Navbar
